gates.name: rz
gates.qasm_def: gate rz(theta) q { U(0, 0, theta) q; }

gates.name: sx
gates.qasm_def: gate sx q { U(pi/2, 3*pi/2, pi/2) q; }

gates.name: x
gates.qasm_def: gate x q { U(pi, 0, pi) q; }

gates.name: ecr
gates.qasm_def: gate ecr q0, q1 { U(pi, pi/2, 7*pi/2) q0; U(pi, 7*pi/2, pi/2) q1; CX q0, q1; U(0, 0, 7*pi/2) q0; U(pi/2, 7*pi/2, pi/2) q1; }
